# Xcode and Swift .gitignore

## Build generated
build/
DerivedData/

## Xcode
*.xcworkspace
xcuserdata/

## Swift Package Manager
.build/

## CocoaPods
Pods/

## Carthage
Carthage/Build/

## Fastlane
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/Preview.html
fastlane/screenshots/**/*.png
fastlane/test_output

## Accidental local files
*.DS_Store
*.swp
*.lock
*.xcuserstate

## Playground files
timeline.xctimeline
playground.xcworkspace
